---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";

const lastUpdated = "2026-06-27";
---

<Base title="Terms of Service | OSCEN" description="Terms governing your use of oscen.ai.">
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 mb-12">
      <p class="reveal text-[10px] font-mono text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="reveal font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem)] text-text-primary leading-[0.9]">
        Terms of<br />
        <span class="italic gradient-text">service.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-text-secondary mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed">
        The ground rules for using oscen.ai. Plain English, short.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-6">
      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">About these terms</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          By using oscen.ai you agree to these terms. The site is operated by Rio Bold LLC.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">What you can do</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Read the site, submit a form, subscribe to the newsletter, follow links to demos, and support the project at <a href="/support" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">/support</a>. Personal and non-commercial use is welcome.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">What you cannot do</h2>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Scrape the site at scale or impose disproportionate load.</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse engineer anything (the brain demos included).</li>
          <li>Impersonate us or our team.</li>
          <li>Use the site to do anything illegal.</li>
          <li>Attempt to disrupt the site's operation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Intellectual property</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The site content (writing, designs, brain visualization, illustrations) is owned by Rio Bold LLC or licensed to us. The OSCEN technology itself (the neuromorphic brain, the source code, the trained model state, the patent-pending architecture) is proprietary. Nothing on this site grants you a license to that technology.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Forms and inquiries</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          When you submit a form you are sharing information voluntarily. We may use it to respond to you and to follow up with related opportunities (for example, replying to a newsletter signup with an investor brief if you indicated interest). See the <a href="/privacy" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Investor inquiries</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The investor surfaces on this site (including <a href="/invest" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">/invest</a> and the materials linked from it) are for informational purposes only. They are not an offer of securities. Any actual offering of securities will be made only to qualified investors through formal documentation, in compliance with applicable securities laws.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Third-party links</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Some links go to external sites (Stripe, scientific papers, social media). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">No warranty</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The site is provided "as is." We make no guarantees about uptime, accuracy of forward-looking statements, or fitness for any particular purpose.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Rio Bold LLC's liability arising from your use of this site is limited to the amount you paid us in the past 12 months (typically zero).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Governing law</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The laws of the State of Wyoming, United States, apply. Disputes go to the state and federal courts located in Wyoming.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We may update these terms. The "Last updated" date will change.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <a href="mailto:info@oscen.ai" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">info@oscen.ai</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm pt-4">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p class="pt-2">
        <a href="/" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">&larr; Back to home</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
